snippet.title: Insignificant - Little Hero, Big Adventure! (Release Trailer)
snippet.description:
Insignificant is the story-focused indie Action-RPG in your backyard that plays with your perspective and lets you rediscover our world from a new point of view: three inches tall. Poke enemies with a fork, cover yourself in tinfoil armor, and try not to get mauled by raccoons!

Insignificant Is Available Now On Steam!
http://bit.ly/INSIGNIFICANT
